{
  "texts": [
    "The algorithm obtained competitive performance in comparison with other search methods such as PSO and FA for solving 24 numerical test functions.",
    "A comprehensive survey of the Tree Seed Algorithm was conducted by [35] where a variety of variants of Tree Seed Algorithm were analysed.",
    "The variant methods included the combination of Tree Seed Algorithm with other swarm intelligence algorithms such as Artificial Bee Colony (ABC) [36] and SCA.",
    "Improvement strategies such as Levy and Gaussian distributions were also utilized to enhance flexibility of Tree Seed Algorithm.",
    "Moreover, the effectiveness of Tree Seed Algorithm was also ascertained by handling a variety of real-world optimization problems such as feature selection and image compression."
  ]
}